# Assets Directory

This directory should contain the following image files for the mobile app:

- `icon.png` (1024x1024) - App icon
- `splash.png` (1242x2436) - Splash screen
- `adaptive-icon.png` (1024x1024) - Android adaptive icon
- `favicon.png` (48x48) - Web favicon
- `notification-icon.png` (96x96) - Notification icon

You can generate these assets using:
- Design tools like Figma, Sketch, or Adobe XD
- Online icon generators
- Expo's asset generation tools

For now, you can use placeholder images or the Expo default assets.
